      "id": "note--team24-analysis",
      "created": "2026-04-05T02:00:00.000Z",
      "modified": "2026-04-05T02:00:00.000Z",
      "content": "TEAM24 is a multi-operator phishing syndicate targeting South Korean platform credentials. 10 named operators run 9 campaigns across 7 platforms. Open directory at arnptec.com exposes full operation structure. Possible but unconfirmed overlap with DPRK-linked Kimsuky campaigns targeting Naver/Kakao users. LOW-MEDIUM confidence attribution.",
